{"tid":1016114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"約303萬人次進出香港   零售業界：旺丁不旺財","createTime":"2019-02-10T15:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T00:03:21.000Z","uid":13869,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2b00d59280fabc4043765c43e9ce97073b2abbdc","tid":1016114,"uid":13869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T15:00:51.000Z","msg":"【張建宗：初一至初三約303萬人次進出香港】<br />\n【零售業界：旺丁不旺財】<br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗指，初一至初三期間，有約303萬人次進出香港，較去年同期增加約兩成。港珠澳大橋及高鐵西九站，出入境人次亦創通車以來新高。旅客人數增加，不過零售業界指旺丁不旺財，生意比去年差。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #張建宗 #港珠澳大橋 #高鐵西九站 #旺丁不旺財<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1052505911608143?sfns=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1052505911608143%3Fsfns%3D1&d=rjg6%2Bw4p6Mv2XY9C6AOo51tf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=3e240017\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1052505911608143?sfns=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">旺丁不旺財！！<br />\n冇撚經濟貢獻呀！！<br />\n見到啲喼都燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f1c770d2d76c19486796b8c80d217612bdbde71b","tid":1016114,"uid":41389,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T15:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e7GYK39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe7GYK39.png&h=f63b433d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca6e44201cb3b6525216e416c442fa8b36c37c84","tid":1016114,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T15:19:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88561ea1cf76a28f5773e73f10f0e136c2403803","tid":1016114,"uid":56698,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T15:29:49.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"574fd9d2732e880ab38968c49ceefb3c60c717a8","tid":1016114,"uid":181111,"like":0,